name: RIVIERA Necklace Set
description: Very pretty, 17” genuine Sponge Coral, Turquoise glass beads and small Hematite rounds make up this lovely design! All strung on top quality, flexible jeweler’s wire and secured with a pretty heart toggle clasp! SET comes beautifully boxed! Comes with the matching 1 & 3/4” earrings on Sterling Silver French ear wires! If you need a different size, please let me know!

name: GARDEN PARTY Necklace Set
description:
Very classy 17 & 1/2” necklace with genuine 13×9mm Rhodochrosite beads, 8mm & 6mm genuine Moldavite rounds, NonMagnetic Hematite and silver-plated spacers, all strung on top quality, flexible  jeweler’s wire and secured with a pretty toggle clasp!

	The matching 2” earrings are of the exact same materials and are suspended from sterling silver ear wires! Complete set comes beautifully boxed!

name: CHERRY BOMB Bracelet
description: Very pretty 7 & 1/2” bracelet with Cherry Red Glass beads, Hex Black Hematite rondelles and silver-plated round spacers…finished off with a “super powerful” magnetic clasp for easy on, but “won’t” fall off! This bracelet, like ALL my jewelry, is strung on top quality, flexible jeweler’s wire for durability and easy wearing!

name: BLACK TIE AFFAIR Necklace Set
description: Gorgeous 18” double-strand necklace with “vintage” Monet glass pearl beads and genuine Swarovski Crystals, finished off with a lobster claw clasp! The beautiful pendant that suspends from the necklace is a Genuine 20cttw. Cushion Cut Black Onyx gemstone surrounded by 24 “individually” set genuine White Topaz gems in 925 Sterling Silver! If that were’nt enough, this necklace comes with the matching 1 & 3/4” earrings on sterling silver lever back ear wires! Entire set comes beautifully boxed and ready to GIVE or WEAR!

name: SIESTA Turquoise Earrings
description: Beautiful 2 & 1/4” genuine Turquoise and Hematite earrings with silver-plated round spacers on Sterling Silver French ear wires! These are a knock out!
